divs: Sighting DetailsJust seeiing some friends off from our house when we saw the strange circules around the full moon (this happened before Christmas 2005.) Then to day downloaded the picures to Fireworks to look at them and print them out. It was then that I noticed this strange object in two of the four pictures, I thought it was fluff of the lens but it is only on two pictures and no others and the aspect is different in each of them. What is it? A Satalight! or something else!!!!
